{"tid":1613672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去完cwb有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:36:28.000Z","uid":174496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a2fec043a9398b40555fbfec03c0357e5d1482","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"一開始成班人企係到嗌口號，然後龍頭走咗去time square嗰度唱歌，再走返去sogo嗰邊佔馬路。我覺得可以一齊真行街而唔係淨係喺cwb兜圈。<br />\n<br />\n其實可以諗下一齊入sogo行下街，又有冷氣又有舖頭行又有得試食，不過記住<span style=\"color: red;\">只行唔買</span>，逼爆sogo，搞到sogo提前落閘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我覺得佔馬路唔係咁好，會影響自己人走。快閃集會應該要散嘅時候全部人都可以盡快離開，如果塞住馬路<span style=\"color: red;\">一黎會冇車走有狗黎就難走，二黎會變相鼓勵人搭黨鐵。</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得快閃集合係比大家快聚快散，唔係留低打陣地戰。仲有大家集會嘅時候嗌口號同唱歌之餘，可以做埋個只行唔買嘅消費者，塞9住sogo。<br />\n<br />\n點睇？<br />\n<br />\n講得唔好嘅話屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0f9189d1aeb5e4a6cf9968bc79f0a4e870f9e8","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"毒撚開po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b97e5aa8ea3ab427522c2eb3da93bfe87576f6c","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"d3d8923954fa987c3b735bb142509229f8dddc0b","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c3fd94d01c3f24892e8688b19ec04ebb24058707","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5230ff6462d5ccf1d5cf311474b484c82f6b29df","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8a3e696f54330ad50b417f3fe740b6c879a0d08a","tid":1613672,"uid":174496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:34